    <name>FreeCAD Cloud Browser</name>
    <description>Browse and open files from S3-compatible storage (Amazon S3, MinIO, Wasabi, etc.), FTP/SFTP servers, and WebDAV/Nextcloud servers directly from FreeCAD — no manual download/upload needed. Supports access-key authentication for S3, username/password or SSH key for FTP/SFTP, and basic/digest auth for WebDAV.</description>

